title: 'Best product'
body: I bought 2-3 of these for my construction sites and they last for a very long time.  The only thing missing is a magnetic latch so that it can stick to metal objects (H beam or I beam or C channels) that are at a height.  The only thing that we need to take care of, is that it should be cleaned and wiped if it gets wet or dirty.  The spring works well if it doesn't get wet and starts to rust.  This one has been with me for well over 6-8 months.  It should easily last for more than 2 years if maintained well.  I had bought one 3 years ago and it lasted for more than 2 years.  The measurements are accurate and it functions well even after a year or so.  It will definitely not survive a fall of more than 4-5 metres.

body: 'The media could not be loaded. The locking mechanism is very good. Comes handy if you are working alone and no one is there to hold the tape with you.
